title: Im Stuck On A Champion Rotation
body: Im stuck on the champion rotation of: Darius, Shyvana, Brand, Ashe, Garen, Katarina, Leona, Miss Fortune, Ryze and Varus. Someone help me please.

replies.body: Ya they changed some things. Check out the [New Player Guide over here](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/site/guide/champions.html).
if your under level 6 then thats the free champion roation you start out with :)
